{"tid":1630451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求大家係民主法案通過前忍耐","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:12.000Z","uid":222453,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0f119c3f1704e567ad5aa631421b728d5f420e9a","tid":1630451,"uid":222453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:20.000Z","msg":"知大家好難忍垃圾黑警藍絲<br />\n但依家我地真係真係好需要輿論支持 國際支持<br />\n求大家忍一陣 以武制暴係安全隱蔽情況下進行<br />\n在此請了🙏🏻🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"59955f03c0789a759691a14b94ef2dfcf40ada00","tid":1630451,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f597be9be7c41f9dfca68f06e59e4b77d6045e1","tid":1630451,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"其實我唔明個邏輯<br />\n<br />\n乜唔係示威情況越激烈<br />\n正正代表冇嘢制裁到班狗官<br />\n所以更加需要通過人權法咩？"},{"pid":"481fb15244d5d5e5674169ad9bc40831137372f4","tid":1630451,"uid":254596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01e4a0844cf72c7a307dc038b2e32a7931e81d4a","tid":1630451,"uid":121548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"721 811 831 新屋嶺"},{"pid":"4090d1db26a8df93ca9514ff5b2f4efd16214fae","tid":1630451,"uid":257398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"對 唔差在幾日，唔好無咗之前嘅付出"},{"pid":"d853fa34d31abf325519f15fe2d2f50fb12b3998","tid":1630451,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得會同法案通過有關係？你覺得美國會因為你爆幾塊玻璃而唔過法案？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0766e0e8adf5ef51dc4419b375be47ae8505460d","tid":1630451,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1669438c0aeb3b3746aa5d799582f53ba2cab1dc","tid":1630451,"uid":280475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"1ccab34654ba76f6f04e51b8031eff0b8ee4ea96","tid":1630451,"uid":33099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"唔好當外國盲啦<br />\n<br />\n一出蒙面法已經成堆國家出聲明叫特區政府唔好火上加油<br />\n<br />\nAnyway 大家冷靜 d 等人權法過左先我又唔反對既"},{"pid":"f890a05803a7bc81248c57273c13c7f81aa96b5b","tid":1630451,"uid":222453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"f338815cae2d1a8381e1691326718fff87a51494